author: Reuters Editorial
title: China's U.S. envoy says trade deal being implemented, hopes for coordinated response
description: China is still implementing the first phase of a Sino-U.S. trade pact, its ambassador to the United States said, but hoped the two could work together to assess the changing situation and coordinate their response, the Global Times said on Sunday.
